msgid "Tardu,"
"\n"
"\nMother didn't believe me. Said there's no such thing as thorn-covered zombies. "
"\n"
"\nWell, when the zombies eat everyone on the farm, then she'll believe me!"
"\n"
"\n—Solly Gaudet"
