"\n"
"\nI request carts to retrieve the statuary you delivered. The gargoyles are indeed fine representations of that race, too fine perhaps. They have attracted the attention, perhaps amorous, of a live gargoyle. The statues must be returned."
"\n"
"\nMy guards are fending off the creature, but it is becoming increasingly irate. I do not know for how long we"
